fields.name: Category
fields.description: Workbook category, as defined by the user at creation time.

fields.name: DisplayName
fields.description: The user-defined name of the private workbook.

fields.name: SerializedData
fields.description: Configuration of this particular private workbook. Configuration data is a string containing valid JSON

fields.name: SourceId
fields.description: Optional resourceId for a source resource.

fields.name: Tags
fields.description: A list of 0 or more tags that are associated with this private workbook definition

fields.name: TimeModified
fields.description: Date and time in UTC of the last modification that was made to this private workbook definition.

fields.name: UserId
fields.description: Unique user id of the specific user that owns this private workbook.

fields.name: Version
fields.description: This instance's version of the data model. This can change as new features are added that can be marked private workbook.
